    "body": "Hey - I'm new to this thread and fairly new to Ethereum contracts. But I have several years of experience in subscription billing. I'm one of the team that created the [Kill Bill ](http://killbill.io/) open source subscription billing project. I have also taught a course at S[tanford on Subscription Billing](https://www.slideshare.net/MartinWesthead/building-innovative-subscriptionbased-businesses-lecture-1). There's a lot of potential complexity here that I have recently been starting to think about. I totally agree with the idea of keeping things simple to begin with, but it would be great to build in extensibility. I'd love to help.",
